'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales sun damu da cewa za a iya kiransu 'yan wasan Muppets
Wasu 'yan majalisa sun nuna rashin amincewarsu da shawarar sauya lakabi zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Dalilin haka shi ne shirin sauya sunan majalisar zuwa Welsh Parliament (Majalisar Wales).
'Yan majalisa na dukkan bangarorin siyasa suna tsoron kada a yi musu ba'a.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Labour ya ce kungiyarsa na damuwa saboda sunan  yana da ma'anar Twp da Pwp.
Ga masu karatu da ba 'yan Wales ba: A cikin Welsh twp yana nufin doof da pwp don Aa.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Plaid Cymru ya ce dukkanin jam'iyyar ba ta farin ciki da hakan ba kuma ya bayar da shawarwari.
Wani memba na Jam'iyyar Conservative ta Wales ya ce kungiyarsa tana da farin ciki game da sauya sunan amma ya nuna babban kamanceceniya tsakanin MWP da Muppet.
A wannan mahallin, ana furta harafin Welsh w kamar yadda ake furta harafin u a Turanci da ake magana a Yorkshire.
Hukumar Majalisar, wacce ke shirin tsara dokar sauya sunan, ta ce: "Hakika, yanke shawara kan sunayen 'yan majalisar ta karshe na 'yan majalisar ne".
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba da izinin Majalisar Wakilai ta Wales ta canza sunanta.
A watan Yuni, kwamitin ya fitar da sakamakon wani sauraron jama'a game da shawarwarin, wanda ya nuna goyon baya mai yawa ga sunan Welsh Parliament ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya.
Game da taken 'yan majalisa, ƙungiyar ta fi son Welsh Parliament Members ko WMPs, yayin da a cikin sauraron jama'a, zaɓi MWP ya sami goyon baya mafi yawa.
'Yan majalisa na ganin za su ba da shawarwari a kan wasu hanyoyin, amma fafutukar neman yarjejeniya ga shugaban majalisar Elin Jones, wanda za a gabatar da kudurin doka a cikin makonni, na iya zama matsala.
Dokar ta kawo sauye-sauye kan yadda majalisar za ta yi aiki, ciki har da dokokin hana 'yan majalisar shiga majalisar da kuma tsarin kwamitocin.
A lokacin da 'yan majalisa ke muhawara kan dokar, za su iya kada kuri'ar ƙarshe a kan sunayensu.
'Yan Macedonia sun kada kuri'ar raba gardama kan sauya sunan kasar
Masu jefa kuri'a za su yanke shawara ranar Lahadi ko za su sauya sunan kasarsu zuwa Jamhuriyar Arewacin Macedonia.
An shirya zaben ne domin sasanta wata takaddama da ta shafe shekaru da dama da makwabciyar kasar Girka, wadda ke da lardin da take da suna makwabciyar ta Macedonia.
Athens ta dade tana dagewa cewa sunan makwabciyarta ta arewa yana nuna cewa tana da'awar yankin Girka, kuma ta yi magana akai-akai game da shigar da ita cikin EU da NATO.
Shugaban kasar Macedonia Gjorge Ivanov, wanda ya yi adawa da kuri'ar raba gardamar da aka yi kan sauya sunan kasar, ya ce ba zai amince da kuri'ar ba.
Amma magoya bayan zaben, ciki har da Firaministan kasar Zoran Zaev, sun ce sauya sunan shi ne kudin da za a biya don shiga kungiyar tarayyar Turai da NATO.
