Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron karar Brett Kavanaugh
Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar da aka yi a ranar Alhamis a gidajen talabijin shida na kasar, na wanda aka zaba a Kotun Koli, Brett Kavanaugh da matarsa, Christine Blasey Ford, wanda ta zarge shi da cin zarafin mata a shekarun 1980.
A halin yanzu, harkar siyasa ta ci gaba da tabarbarewa, kuma gidajen talabijin sun dakatar da shirin su na yau da kullum a ranar Juma'a saboda wani abu da ya faru a minti na karshe: yarjejeniyar da Jeff Flake, Sanata daga Arizona, ya yi da ta ce FBI ta gudanar da binciken da ya shafi zargin na mako guda.
Ford ya shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai cewa ya tabbata 100% cewa Kavanaugh ya bugu a wani biki na makarantar sakandare, ya matsa mata kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin cire tufafinta.
Kavanaugh ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa mai cike da sha'awa cewa ya tabbata cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila fiye da miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ya ruwaito sun kalli sauraron.
Kamfanin ya gano matsakaicin yawan masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ga sauran cibiyoyin sadarwa kamar PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network waɗanda suka watsa sauraron, ba a sami lambobin nan da nan ba.
Ƙari ga haka, Nielsen tana yawan samun matsala wajen auna yawan masu sauraro a ofisoshinsa.
Don a kwatanta wannan, wannan ya yi daidai da yawan masu kallo a wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko kuma bikin Oscar.
Tashar Fox News Channel, wacce masu gabatar da labarai masu ra'ayi suka goyi bayan zaben Kavanaugh, ta sami matsakaicin yawan masu kallo na rana daya, miliyan 5.69 a cewar Nielsen.
ABC ta zo ta biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS ta samu masu kallo miliyan 3.1 bisa ga Nielsen, NBC miliyan 2.94, MSNBC miliyan 2.89 da CNN miliyan 2.52.
Amma bayan an gama sauraron jawabin, mutane sun ci gaba da nuna sha'awar.
Flake ne babban jigon wasan kwaikwayon na ranar Juma'a.
Bayan ofishin mai mulkin mallaka ya fitar da wata sanarwa da ke nuna cewa zai kada kuri'ar Kavanaugh, an kama shi a kan kyamarorin CNN da CBS a safiyar ranar Juma'a, yayin da masu zanga-zangar ke tursasa shi a cikin lif a kan hanyarsa zuwa sauraron shari'a.
