Mexico AMLO ta yi alkawarin ba za ta yi amfani da sojoji kan fararen hula ba
Zababben shugaban kasar Mexico Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin ba zai taba amfani da karfin soji kan fararen hula ba, yayin da ake gabatowa da cika shekaru 50 da zubar da jini a kan dalibai a kasarsa.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin a ranar Asabar a Tlatelolco Plaza cewa "ba zai taba amfani da sojoji don zaluntar mutanen Mexico ba".
A ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 1968, sojoji sun harbi mutane 300 a filin da ake zanga-zangar lumana, kuma a lokacin, ƙungiyoyin ɗalibai masu hagu suna ci gaba a duk faɗin Latin Amurka.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin tallafawa matasa 'yan Mexico ta hanyar ba da tallafin kowane wata ga dalibai da kuma bude wasu jami'o'in gwamnati kyauta.
Ya ce rashin aikin yi da rashin samun ilimi ya sa matasa suka shiga cikin ƙungiyoyin 'yan bindiga.
Ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take baiwa AI
A cewar mai saka jari kuma mai aikin kera kere-kere Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple, a yayin da kasar Sin ke kara aiki a fannin kera kere, ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take kashewa wajen bincike a fannin.
Wannan bayanin ya biyo bayan sanarwar AI daga sassan gwamnati daban-daban na Amurka, duk da cewa Amurka gabaɗaya ba ta da wata dabarar AI.
A shekarar da ta gabata, kasar Sin ta bayyana shirinta na zama kasa ta daya a fannin kirkire-kirkire na AI nan da shekarar 2030.
Abin da zai taimaka wajen fara bincike kan AI shi ne ninka kasafin kudin da ake kashewa wajen bincike kan AI, saboda sauran kasashe sun fi Amurka baya.
A wannan makon, Lee ya shaida wa CNBC cewa ninka kudaden da ake bayarwa zai ninka yiwuwar samun babbar nasara a fannin kera kere-kere a Amurka.
Lee, wanda littafinsa mai suna AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order, Houghton Mifflin Harcourt ya wallafa a wannan watan, shi ne shugaban kamfanin Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin kera kere-kere a kasar Sin, Face++.
A cikin shekarun 1980s, ya yi aiki a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon a kan tsarin AI wanda ya doke ɗan wasan Othello na Amurka mafi girma. Daga baya ya zama babban jami'in gudanarwa a Microsoft Research kuma shugaban ofishin Google a China.
Lee ya yaba da gasa ta fasaha ta gwamnatin Amurka kamar Gasar Robotics ta Hukumar Kula da Ayyukan Bincike ta Tsaro (DARPA) kuma ya tambayi lokacin gasar ta gaba, saboda yana son taimakawa wajen gano masu hangen nesa na gaba.
Lee ya ce masu bincike a Amirka suna aiki tuƙuru don su sami tallafin gwamnati.
Ba kasar Sin ce ke karbar manyan malamai ba, amma kamfanoni ne, in ji Lee.
A cikin 'yan shekarun nan, Facebook da Google da kuma wasu kamfanonin fasaha sun ɗauki wasu jami'o'i da yawa da za su yi aiki a kan AI.
Lee ya ce, sauya manufofin ƙaura na Amirka zai iya taimaka wa aikin AI na Amirka.
