LeBron kafin buga wasan farko da Lakers a ranar Lahadi a San Diego
Ga magoya bayan da ke son ganin LeBron James yana buga wa Los Angeles Lakers wasa na farko, jiran zai zo karshe.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa a ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma ba a san yawan mintuna da zai yi a wasan ba.
"Zai zama fiye da daya kuma ƙasa da 48", in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Mai ba da rahoto na Lakers Mike Trudell ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai yi wasa na 'yan mintoci kaɗan ne kawai.
A farkon makon nan, bayan an kammala atisayen, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na wasannin Lakers na wasanni shida.
Ya ce, "Ba na bukatar wasannin farko na kakar wasa a wannan lokaci na aiki don shirya kaina".
Lokaci don taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara taron yakin neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia, a daren yau.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin gangamin da Trump ya shirya yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da wasu wuraren da ake sonsa kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
A yayin da ake fuskantar zaben tabbatar da zabensa a Kotun Koli, Trump na son samun goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a majalisar.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron Trump a yammacin Virginia, kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon shi a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, a yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018, da karfe 7:00 na yamma (lokacin Gabas).
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a yammacin Virginia a YouTube a ƙasa.
Ana sa ran Trump zai yi jawabi a gaban kotun kolin Amurka kan zargin cin zarafin jima'i da aka yi wa Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi fama da tashin hankali a wannan makon.
Amma babban burin wannan jerin zanga-zangar shine tallafawa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar zaɓe mai wuya a watan Nuwamba.
Don haka, tawagar yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump ta shaida wa Reuters cewa waɗannan gangamin biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa za su taimaka wajen "taro masu sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin ci gaba da karfafa rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai".
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga shirinsa, don haka shugaban zai yi tafiye-tafiye zuwa jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai iya yayin da ake fuskantar yakin neman zabe", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump da bai so a bayyana sunansa ba, ya shaida wa Reuters.
A cewar West Virginia Metro News, ana sa ran masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania za su halarci taron da aka shirya a gidan wasan Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling da yammacin yau, kuma kafofin watsa labarai daga Pittsburgh za su ba da rahoto.
Ziyarar da Trump ya kai a ranar Asabar ita ce ta biyu da ya kai a wannan watan a jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe da kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin tallafawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican daga West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ya ragu a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo don ya yi kokarin kara masa karfi a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, kamar yadda Reuters ta ruwaito.
Ryder Cup 2018: Tawagar Amurka ta nuna aniyar yaki don ci gaba da fatan samun nasarar gasar a ranar Lahadi
Bayan zagaye uku na wasa guda, wasannin hudu da aka yi a ranar Asabar da yamma, wataƙila su ne abin da gasar Ryder ta ke bukata.
Wannan motsi na motsi na motsi a matsayin wasan kwaikwayo na wasanni shine kawai ƙwarewa, amma wanda 'yan wasan suka gaskata da gaske, musamman a wasanni kamar wannan.
To, ina kuke ganin wannan ci gaba yake yanzu?
Sun kasance a kan maki shida, kuma yanzu sun kai hudu, don haka ina tsammanin wannan yana ba mu ɗan ƙarfi, in ji Jordan Spieth yayin barin filin wasa.
A gaskiya, Turai tana da fifiko, tana da maki huɗu a gaba, kuma akwai maki goma sha biyu a baya.
Amma Spieth ya ce Amurkawa na jin iska a cikin jirgin ruwan kuma suna da dalilin jin daɗin, ba wai kawai yanayin Spieth da Justin Thomas ba, waɗanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma kowannensu na iya samun maki uku daga cikin huɗu.
Spieth ya kasance mai ƙarfi daga tsalle zuwa kore kuma yana ci gaba da yin misali mai kyau.
Muryar farin ciki ta kara daɗaɗa yayin da ya ci gaba da zagaye, lokacin da ya yi wani muhimmin kwallo don yanke shawara game na huɗu da maki huɗu ga duka biyun, bayan shi da Thomas sun rage biyu bayan ramuka biyu.
A rami na 15, kwallo da ya buga ya yanke musu wasa, kuma hakan ya sa 'yan wasan Amurka suka yi ihu.
Spieth ya ce, "Ina bukatar in durƙusa in kula da kaina".
Wannan shi ne abin da kowane ɗan wasa ya rage.
Akwai ramuka 18 don yin alama.
Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood ne kawai 'yan wasa da suka zira kwallaye fiye da Spieth da Thomas a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata, kuma babu shakka sun rubuta tarihin gasar Ryder.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta biyu da ba ta da kyau, amma suna da maki huɗu cikin huɗu kuma ba za su yi kuskure ba.
MOLIVOUD ba su ne kawai ma'aurata da ba su buga bogey ba a ranar Asabar da rana, amma sun kuma kauce wa bogey a ranar Asabar da safe, Jumma'a da rana, da kuma ramuka tara na karshe a ranar Jumma'a.
Wannan jerin da kuma yadda ake ganin an samu kuzari a tsakanin su da kuma masu sauraro da ke cikin taron sun tabbatar da cewa su ne 'yan wasan da za su doke ranar Lahadi.
Zai fi kyau duka biyun a lokaci guda a ramuka daban-daban.
Amma ba zai dace mu yi magana game da ɗaukakar Turai ba.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi taƙaitaccen gwaji tare da Sergio Garcia, jarumin safiya na hudu, wanda ke wasa tare da Alex Noren.
Wani bogey da biyu biyu a ramuka tara na gaba sun jefa Spaniards da Swedes cikin matsala da ba za su iya shawo kan su ba.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai iya taimaka musu.
Hudu da kuma nau'i-nau'i na hudu suna da ban sha'awa sosai saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin ma'aurata, shawarwarin da suke bayarwa ko ba su bayar ba, da kuma yadda dabarun zasu iya canzawa cikin sauri.
'Yan Turai sun fi kowa kyau a matsayin tawagarsu, kuma suna kan gaba a rana ta karshe, amma wannan zagaye na hudu ya nuna cewa tawagar Amurka ta shirya don yin gwagwarmaya, abin da wasu, musamman a Amurka, suka yi shakkarsa.
Turai ta ci gaba da cin nasara a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup da ci 10 da 6
Turai ta ci gaba da samun ci gaba da ci 10 da 6 a wasan da ta buga a ranar Asabar da Amurka, kuma ta ci gaba da samun ci gaba a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder.
Gwarzon 'yan wasan Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun ci Tiger Woods da ke fama da kalubale da nasara biyu, kuma sun samu maki hudu a gasar Le Golf National.
Kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Turai wadda Thomas Bjørn ke jagoranta, tana neman dawo da kofin da ta rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta yi nasara a wasan hudu da safe a kan tawagar Amurka da ke wasa da rashin kyau, kuma ta lashe jerin da 3-1.
A wasannin hudu, Amurka ta yi tsayayya sosai kuma ta ci wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya ci gaba da kasancewa a baya ba.
Jim Furyk ya bukaci maki takwas a wasan da suka buga a ranar Lahadi domin ya ci kofin.
Fleetwood ya zama farkon sabon dan Turai da ya ci kwallaye hudu a jere, yayin da shi da Molinari, waɗanda aka yi wa lakabi da Molliwood bayan ƙarshen mako mai ban sha'awa, suka zama biyu kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup don samun maki hudu a wasanninsu huɗu na farko.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a cikin hudu, sun yi aiki tare da kyau kuma sun doke Woods da aka yi da shi da kuma sabon dan Amurka Bryson Dechambeau tare da 5 & 4 mai ban mamaki.
Woods, wanda ya sha wahala a wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna kwarewarsa a wasu lokatai, amma yanzu ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasanni 29 da ya buga a wasanni hudu da hudu, kuma bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya huta a lokacin hudu da safe, ya dawo ya yi wasa a matsayin abokin tarayya na Henrik Stenson a wasanni hudu.
Amma a wannan rana mai daɗi da iska a kudu maso yammacin birnin Paris, Turai ta fuskanci matsaloli.
Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, wadanda suka lashe gasar zakarun Amurka sau uku, sun kafa wa 'yan wasan Amurkawa misali mai kyau da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun ci nasara a cikin hudu a kan Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter na Spain kuma sun doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy a cikin hudu 4 & 3 bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
A tarihin gasar Ryder Cup, sau biyu ne kawai wata kungiya ta dawo bayan ta yi baya da maki hudu a wasan.
Bayan sun kasance a matsayi na biyu a cikin kwanaki biyu, ba su da alama za su iya kai hari a ranar Lahadi.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi watsi da makaman da ba a amince da su ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa ci gaba da takunkumi ya kara tsananta rashin amincewarsu da Amurka kuma a karkashin wadannan yanayi kasar ba za ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliyarta ba.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron shekara-shekara na kungiyar ta duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "matakai masu muhimmanci" a shekarar da ta gabata, "a matsayin wata kyakkyawar manufa", kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makaman nukiliya, rushe wuraren gwajin nukiliya da kuma yin alkawarin ba za ta kara yawan makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya ba.
Amma ba mu ga amsar Amurka ba, in ji shi.
Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, ba za a amince da tsaron kasa ba, kuma a karkashin wannan yanayi ba za mu fara kwashe makamai ba.
Yayin da Ri ya maimaita korafin da Koriya ta Arewa ta yi game da adawar Washington da tsarin 'mataki-mataki' na haramta makaman nukiliya, inda za a ba Koriya ta Arewa lada don matakai masu zuwa, maganarsa ta zama mai mahimmanci saboda ba ta yi watsi da haramta makaman nukiliya ba kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi nuni da wata sanarwa ta hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong-un da Donald Trump suka yi a taron farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, inda Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki kan "kawar da makaman nukiliya daga yankin Koriya ta Kudu", yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin ba da tabbacin tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa na son kawo karshen yakin Koriya da aka yi daga shekarar 1950 zuwa 1953, yayin da Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara watsi da makaman nukiliyarta.
Bugu da ƙari, Washington ta yi tsayayya da bukatar sassauta takunkumin da ƙasashen duniya suka kakaba wa Koriya ta Arewa.
Amurka ta nace akan duniyar nukiliya da farko, ta kara matsa lamba ta hanyar takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar tilastawa, har ma ta yi adawa da ayyana karshen yaki, in ji Ri.
Gaskiyar cewa takunkumi zai iya sa mu durƙusa shi ne tunanin mutanen da ba su san kome game da mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, tsauraran takunkumi na kara tsananta mana rashin amincewa.
Ri bai bayyana shirin taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump ba, wanda shugaban Amurka ya bayyana a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon nan.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya nuna cewa akwai tarurruka uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya kara da cewa: Idan Koriya ta Kudu ce ta kasance ita ce ta biyu a batun haramta makaman nukiliya maimakon Amurka, to da ba a samu wannan cikas ba a batun haramta makaman nukiliya a yankin Koriya.
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ris ya sha bamban da jawabinsa a bara, lokacin da ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ba makawa ne Koriya ta Arewa ta harba makamai masu linzami zuwa Amurka bayan da shugaba Trump ya kira Kim a matsayin "mutumin makami mai linzami" a kan aikin kashe kansa.
A wannan shekarar, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar "hallaka" Koriya ta Arewa, ya yaba wa Kim a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya saboda ƙarfin hali game da matakan kawar da makamai, amma ya ce akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da sanya takunkumi har sai an kawar da makaman nukiliya na Koriya ta Arewa.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da lokacin da zai yi hakan: Ko zai ɗauki shekara biyu, shekara uku ko watanni biyar  ba kome.
China da Rasha sun ce Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta bukaci Pyongyang ta ba da lada kan matakan da ta dauka.
Sai dai sakataren harkokin wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya shaida wa kwamitin tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis cewa: A kowane hali, tilasta dokar hana fita daga kwamitin tsaro dole ne a ci gaba da aiki da karfi har sai mun cimma cikakken, tabbatacce kuma tabbataccen haramta makaman nukiliya.
Majalisar Tsaro ta kara tsaurara takunkumi kan Koriya ta Arewa tun shekara ta 2006 domin dakile ayyukan nukiliya da makaman nukiliya na Pyongyang.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a gefen babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, sannan ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron kolin na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma tafiyarsa ta ƙarshe ba ta yi nasara ba.
A watan Yuli, ya ce ya samu ci gaba a lokacin da ya bar Pyongyang, amma bayan sa'o'i kadan Koriya ta Arewa ta zarge shi da yin "buƙatun da suka yi kama da na 'yan daba".
A wata ganawa da Moon a wannan watan, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin rushe sansanin makaman nukiliya da kuma sansanin makaman nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki matakan da suka dace.
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa "matakan da ake son dauka" sun hada da tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya bayar a Singapore da kuma matakan daidaita dangantaka da Washington.
Daliban Harvard sun koyi yadda za su yi barci sosai
Wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard ya tabbatar da cewa duk daliban da ke karatun firamare a wannan shekara za su samu karin barci, kuma hakan ya nuna cewa ba ma son al'adar maza da ke ci gaba da yaduwa, wato shan maganin kafeyin da kuma yin nazari duk dare.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya lura cewa ɗaliban manyan jami'o'i a duniya ba sa kula da kansu.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a fannin maganin bacci a makarantar likitanci ta Harvard da kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da Women's, ne ya tsara wannan darasin kuma ya ce shi ne na farko a Amirka.
An yi wahayi zuwa gare shi ya kafa wannan darasi bayan ya ba da jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci a kan ilmantarwa.
A ƙarshe, wata yarinya ta zo wurina kuma ta tambaye ni, "Me ya sa ban san wannan ba sai yanzu, a shekarata ta ƙarshe?"
Ta ce ba wanda ya taɓa gaya mata muhimmancin barci. Hakan ya ba ni mamaki.
A wannan shekara, an soma koyarwa ta farko da ta bayyana wa ɗalibai yadda yin barci sosai zai taimaka musu su yi nasara a makaranta da kuma wasanni.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin tabin hankali a makarantar likitancin Harvard kuma darektan kula da lafiyar jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan darasi ne bayan ta lura da cewa dalibai suna fama da matsalar rashin bacci a cikin mako.
Wannan darasi na awa ɗaya ya ƙunshi ayyuka masu ma'ana.
A wani sashe, ɗalibai suna ganin hoton ɗakin kwana kuma suna danna kofunan kofi, labule, takalman motsa jiki da littattafai don samun bayani game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda rashin barci yake shafar wasan motsa jiki da kuma muhimmancin yin barci.
A wani sashe kuma, masu halartar taron sun koyi cewa rashin barci na dogon lokaci yana iya sa mutum ya yi ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, da kuma ciwon daji.
Bayan haka, za a yi amfani da taswirar jami'ar da ke ɗauke da alamomi masu sa tunani don su yi tunani a kan ayyukansu na yau da kullum.
Mun san cewa ba zai canja halayen ɗalibai nan da nan ba.
Amma mun gaskata cewa suna da 'yancin sanin hakan - kamar yadda kai ma kake da 'yancin sanin yadda shan taba sigari zai shafi lafiyarka", in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Ya ce har yanzu ana alfahari da 'kwance aiki' a daren jiya, ya kara da cewa fasahar zamani da matsin lamba da ke ci gaba da yawaitawa a kan dalibai ya sanya rashin bacci ya zama matsala mai girma.
Don tabbatar da samun isashen barci, ya ce, "makamin sirri" na kowane ɗalibi ya kamata ya kasance don yaƙi da damuwa, gajiya, da tsoro, kuma ya hana samun nauyi, domin rashin barci yana sa kwakwalwa ta shiga yanayin yunwa, don haka suna jin yunwa a kowane lokaci.
Raymond So, wani ɗalibi ɗan shekara 19 daga California, wanda ke nazarin ilimin sunadarai da ilimin halittu, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara wannan darasi.
Ya ce wannan darasin ya buɗe masa idanu kuma ya motsa shi ya biɗi wani darasi da zai shafi dukan jami'a.
Ya yi fatan cewa a mataki na gaba, za a bukaci dukkan daliban da ke karatun digiri na biyu su bi irin wannan tsarin kafin su fara karatunsu a jami'ar da ke da gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai su sa wa kansu ƙararrawa don lokacin bacci da lokacin farkawa kuma su san illolin hasken shuɗi wanda ke fitowa daga allon lantarki da hasken LED wanda zai iya lalata sautin circadian wanda ke haifar da matsaloli yayin bacci.
Livingston da Rangers 1:0: Menga ta ci kwallo ta doke dan wasan Gerrard
Rangers sun sake rasa wani wasan waje lokacin da bugun Dolly Menga ga Steven Gerrard ya haifar da rashin nasara 0-1 a Livingston.
Tawagar Ibrox ta nemi nasarar fitar da ita ta farko tun bayan nasarar da suka samu a St. Johnstone da ci 4-1, amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta sha kashi na biyu a wasanni 18 da Gerrard ya buga a matsayin manajan, wanda ya sa tawagar ta kasance maki takwas a baya da Hearts da ke kan gaba a gasar Ladbrokes Premiership.
Menga ya buga da minti bakwai kafin rabin lokaci, kuma Rangers da ba su da ƙarfin zuciya ba su da wata dama ta daidaitawa.
Yayin da Rangers ke faduwa zuwa matsayi na shida, Livingston ya hau zuwa matsayi na uku, yana da nisa a baya da Hibernian.
Har ila yau, 'yan wasan Rangers na fuskantar matsala bayan da aka yi wa alkalin wasa Calum Spence jinya saboda ciwon kai da wani abu da aka jefa daga cikin ɗakin baƙi ya yi.
Gerrard ya yi canje-canje takwas a cikin tawagar, wanda ya wuce Ayr kuma ya kai wasan kusa da na karshe na Betfred Cup.
Holt, a gefe guda, ya ci gaba da kasancewa da 'yan wasan Livingston guda 11 da suka ci Hearts da maki daya a makon da ya gabata, kuma ya kamata ya yi farin ciki da yadda tawagarsa da ta horar da su ta matsa wa abokan hamayyarsu a kowane mataki.
Ko da yake Rangers sun mamaye filin, Livingston ya fi samun nasara idan suna da kwallon.
Da an samu ci a minti biyu da fara wasan, sai da Mengas ya jefa Scott Pittman a raga, amma dan wasan ya rasa damarsa kuma ya rasa.
Sai kuma wani dogon harbi daga Keaghan Jacobs ya kai ga kyaftin Craig Halkett, amma abokin hamayyarsa Alan Lithgow ya samu damar wucewa daga baya.
Rangers sun ci gaba da yin wasa, amma wasan da suka buga a kashi na uku na ƙarshe ya nuna cewa suna da bege maimakon tabbaci.
Alfredo Morelos ya yi tunanin cewa ya kamata a ba shi fansa bayan da ya yi karo da Steven Lawless bayan sa'a 15, amma alƙali Steven Thomson ya ƙi amincewa da korafin ɗan Colombia.
Rangers sun ci kwallo biyu a farkon rabin wasan, amma tsohon mai tsaron ragar Ibrox Liam Kelly bai yi wata matsala ba da Lasana Coulibaly da kuma Ovie Ejaria.
Ko da yake Livingston ya ci kwallo a minti na 34 ba zai dace da wasan ba, babu shakka sun samu wannan kwallo ne saboda aiki tuƙuru da suka yi.
Har ila yau, Rangers ba su iya magance wani ball daga Jacobs a cikin wani misali mai tsawo ba.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya jefa kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya ci gaba da kasancewa da kwanciyar hankali kuma ya zaɓi Menga don kammalawar sauƙi.
Gerrard ya yi aiki a rabin lokaci kuma ya sauya Coulibaly da Ryan Kent. Canjin ya yi tasiri kusan nan da nan lokacin da dan wasan Morelos ya sanya shi a matsayi, amma Kelly mai ban sha'awa ya hau kan layinsa don toshe kwallon.
Livingston, duk da haka, ya ci gaba da sa baƙi su yi wasa daidai da yadda suke so, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna samun dogon ball bayan daya.
Holt da tawagarsa sun iya kara samun nasara a wasan karshe, amma McGregor ya tsaya tsayin daka kuma ya kare Jacobs kafin Lithgow ya harbi kwallo daga kusurwa.
Mai maye gurbin Rangers Glenn Middleton ya bukaci a ba shi bugun bugun daga baya bayan da ya yi wasa da Jacobs, amma Thomson ya sake kallon baya.
