Geiger ya ƙirƙira wata hanya ta gano da kuma auna rediyo, kuma wannan ƙirar ta kai ga na'urar da ake kira Geiger counter.
Daga nan, Geiger counter ya zama misali na kimiyya, kuma ya zama misali na al'adun gargajiya, misali a cikin fim din Bells of Coronado na 1950 tare da masu binciken kiwo Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: "Mene ne wannan?"
Rogers: Wannan Geiger counter ne da ake amfani da shi wajen neman ma'adanai masu saurin gudu kamar uranium.
Idan ka sa waɗannan belun kunne, za ka iya jin tasirin radiation a cikin ma'adanai.
Evans: "A gaskiya, ina jin wani karyewa!
Hans Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, kwanaki kadan kafin ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
