Amurka na iya amfani da sojan ruwanta wajen hana fitar da makamashin Rasha  Ma'aikatar Harkokin Cikin Gida
A cewar Washington Examines, Washington na iya amfani da sojan ruwa idan ya cancanta don hana makamashi daga Rasha isa kasuwannin ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa, aikin da Rasha ke yi a Syria, wata hujja ce ta gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
Ya ce, "Ina ganin ainihin dalilin da ya sa Rasha ke aiki a Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne don neman sabbin kasuwannin samar da makamashi kamar yadda ake yi a Gabashin Turai".
Kuma a cewar jami'in akwai hanyoyin da za a bi da wannan.
"Amurka za ta iya aiki tare da sojan ruwanta don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin teku sun kasance a bude, kuma idan ya cancanta, ta toshe su don tabbatar da cewa makamashi daga Rasha ba zai isa kasuwa ba", in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi jawabi ga mahalarta taron na kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta da ke kiran kanta "muryar masu amfani da wutar lantarki" a Amurka.
Ya kwatanta yadda Washington ke hulɗa da Rasha da Iran, ya kuma lura cewa sun yi kama.
Amfani da maye gurbin man fetur ya fi dacewa a tattalin arziki a Iran da Rasha, in ji shi, yayin da ya bayyana Rasha a matsayin One Trick Pony tare da tattalin arzikin da ke dogara da burbushin halittu.
An yi wannan bayanin ne a lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ke shirin fadada fitar da iskar gas zuwa Turai, ta maye gurbin Rasha, wacce ta fi dacewa ga masu amfani da ita a Turai.
Don haka jami'an gwamnati, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump da kansa, suna kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga aikin bututun mai na Nord Stream 2 wanda Trump ya ce ya mayar da Berlin "bashin" Moscow.
Moscow ta sha jaddada cewa aikin famfo mai daraja dala biliyan 11 da ake kira Nord Stream 2, wanda zai ninka yawan bututun zuwa mita biliyan 110 na bututun, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ya yi jayayya cewa, babbar adawar da Washington ke yi wa aikin, na da nasaba da tattalin arziki kuma misali ne na rashin adalci.
Ina ganin dukkanmu mun yarda cewa bai kamata a yi amfani da makamashi a matsayin hanyar matsa lamba ba, kuma masu amfani da makamashi su zaɓa masu samar da su, inji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Aleksandr Novak bayan ganawa da Ministan Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a watan Satumba a Moscow.
Amurka ta samu matsala daga Jamus, wadda ta tabbatar da alƙawarinta ga aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, BDI, ta bukaci Amurka da ta guji shiga cikin manufofin samar da makamashi na EU da kuma yarjejeniyar kasashen biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
Abu ne mai matukar muhimmanci idan wata kasa ta uku ta tsoma baki a cikin samar da makamashi, in ji shugaban hukumar BDI Dieter Kempf bayan ganawar da shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel ta yi da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
