Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da zalunci ta hanyar tallace-tallacen farfaganda
Mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wata sanarwa mai shafuka hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke bayyana amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi babban birnin kasar Beijing da amfani da kafofin yada labaran Amurka don yada labarai.
Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba da ta gabata game da takardar da aka biya ta China Daily a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a Iowa, bayan da ya zargi China da tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka na ranar 6 ga Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi cewa Beijing ta yi kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya yi daidai da yadda jami'an Amurka suka sanar da Reuters, wani sabon mataki ne na wani kamfen da Washington ta kaddamar don matsa lamba kan China.
A yayin da gwamnatocin kasashen waje ke amfani da tallace-tallace don bunkasa tattalin arziki, Beijing da Washington suna cikin yakin kasuwanci, tare da haraji kan kayayyakin da ke shigowa daga kasashen biyu.
Ana sa ran cewa, takunkumin da China ta dauka a farkon yakin cinikayya zai shafi masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa, wadanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Trump ta Republican, in ji masana kasar Sin da Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa wanda ya dade yana fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta yi wa ma'aikata, masu gonaki da kamfanoni lahani.
China, Branstad ya bayyana a cikin wata sanarwa a jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, yanzu tana kara wannan zalunci ta hanyar tallata tallace-tallace a cikin 'yan jaridar Amurka.
Da yake yada farfagandar sa, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi amfani da al'adar Amurka ta 'yancin magana da kuma 'yan jarida masu zaman kansu ta hanyar tallata tallace-tallace a cikin Des Moines Register, Branstad ya rubuta.
A akasin wannan, za ku ga ƙarancin ra'ayoyi a kan gidajen jarida a nan Beijing, kuma ba za ku ga ainihin ra'ayoyin da jama'ar kasar Sin za su iya yi game da ci gaban tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ba, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna cikin hannun jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin., ya rubuta.
Ya kara da cewa, wata babbar jarida a kasar Sin ta ki karbar tayin buga labarinsa, amma bai bayyana sunan jaridar ba.
