Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a suka kashe, in ji hukumomi.
Saboda rashin sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun bayanai daga gundumar Donggala da ke arewacin Palu ba, wadda ta fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne kuma yana ƙarshen wani ɗan ƙaramin bakin teku a yammacin tekun tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da kimanin mutane 379,800 a cikin 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala yanki ne na gwamnati wanda ke arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi a kan wani yanki na bakin teku mai tsawon kilomita 300 (180 miles).
A cikin gundumar gwamnati, wani yanki ne na gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin lardin, an kiyasta mutane 299,200 suna zaune a cikin 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan hanyoyin samun kudin shiga ga tattalin arzikin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na da muhimmanci a lardin, amma an fi mayar da hankali ne a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta ƙasar Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, girgizar ƙasa da tsunami sun addabi Palu da Donggala sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, mutane fiye da 200 sun mutu a tsunami da ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya addabi yankin Donggala na yamma a shekara ta 1996, kuma mutane tara sun mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa a cikin tekun Pacific.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da ta auku a yammacin lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra a ƙasar Indonesia ta haddasa tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a yankunan da ke gabar tekun Indiya, kusan rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Ƙarƙashin yammacin Sumatra ya yi girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani a ƙarshen watan Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Mutane da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta girgiza kudancin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami da ya auko a gaɓar teku ta kudu, kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane sama da 1,100 aka kashe.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta girgiza tsibirin Mentawai da ke bakin tekun Sumatra kuma ta haddasa tsunami mai tsawon kafa 10.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa mai saurin karyewa ta afkawa gundumar Pidie Jaya da ke Aceh, inda ta haddasa barna da firgici, yayin da mutane ke tunawa da girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane a shekarar 2004.
Amma a wannan lokacin, ba a yi tsunami ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu domin gine-gine da suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok da ke ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta kashe mutane fiye da 500 musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a tsibirin.
An Kama Ɗan Sarah Palin Bisa Zargin Tashin Kan Iyali
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma tsohon dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa, an kama shi ne bisa zargin cin zarafin mutum.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin aikata laifin tashin hankali a gida, hana bayar da rahoton tashin hankali a gida da kuma adawa da hukumomin gwamnati, a cewar wani rahoto da 'yan sanda na Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya nuna cewa ya karɓi wayar wata abokiyarsa sa'ad da ta nemi ta sanar da 'yan sanda.
KTUU ta ce Palin tana tsare a gidan Mat-Su Pretrial Facility kuma an biya ta da belin dala 500.
Ya bayyana a kotu ranar Asabar inda, lokacin da aka tambaye shi game da ikirarinsa, ya amsa da cewa, "Ba shi da laifi, tabbas", in ji hanyar sadarwa.
Ana zargin Palin da aikata laifuffuka uku na Class A, wanda hukuncinsa zai kai shekara guda a gidan yari da kuma tarar dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin da ake kira Class B, wanda ake iya ɗaurin rana ɗaya a kurkuku da kuma tara dala 2,000.
Ba wannan ne karo na farko da aka fara tuhumar Palin ba.
A watan Disamba na shekara ta 2017, an zarge shi da kai wa mahaifinsa Todd Palin hari.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton zargin da ake yi.
Yanzu haka ana shari'ar ne a kotun da ke jihar Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da aikata laifuka da suka shafi tashin hankali a gida, hana bayar da rahoton laifi da kuma mallakar makamai a karkashin tasirin miyagun ƙwayoyi dangane da lamarin.
Abokinsa ta zarge shi da dūkan fuskarta.
A shekara ta 2016, kungiyoyin tsofaffin sojoji sun soki Sarah Palin bayan da ta danganta halin ɗanta ga cutar tashin hankali bayan aikinsa a Iraki.
Tsunami Bayan Girgizar Kasa A Indonesia: Daruruwan Mutane Sun Mutu
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu bayan wata girgizar kasa da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar ƙasar mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta haddasa tsunami da ya halaka dubban gidaje.
An katse wutar lantarki da hanyoyin sadarwa kuma ana tsammanin adadin mutanen da suka mutu zai karu a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar ta auku ne a gabar tekun tsakiyar Sulawesis, da ke arewa maso gabashin babban birnin Indonesia, Jakarta.
Wasu bidiyoyi na lokacin da guguwar ta afkawa kasar suna yawo a shafukan sada zumunta.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru don bikin rairayin bakin teku a birnin Palu sa'ad da tsunami ya afku a bakin tekun.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun bukaci hukuncin kisa ga wadanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York
Masu gabatar da kara a New York sun bukaci a yankewa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake tuhuma da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane takwas, hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa wani ba tun shekarar 1953.
Ana zargin Saipov, mai shekara 30, da yin amfani da wata motar haya ta Home Depot a harin ta'addanci, inda ya hau kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan a watan Oktoba, inda ya buge masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawan keke.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya "kashe" wadanda aka kashe takwas kuma ya "da gangan" ya yi musu mummunan rauni, in ji sanarwar niyyar da aka gabatar a cikin gundumar kudu ta New York.
A cewar takardar kotu, za a iya kashe mutum a kan waɗannan laifuffuka biyu.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun bincike ta kasa ta gabatar da tuhumar Saipov da ke dauke da abubuwa 22 da suka hada da laifuka takwas na kisan kai a cikin mahallin aikata laifuka da aka saba amfani da su a kotunan tarayya a shari'o'in aikata laifuka da aka tsara, da kuma zargin yin amfani da karfi da lalata motoci.
Wannan harin ya bukaci shirye-shiryen da aka yi da gangan, in ji masu gabatar da kara, wadanda suka bayyana yadda Saipov ya aikata laifin a matsayin mugu, mai zalunci da lalata.
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya ba da lahani, zafi da asarar ga iyalai da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji sanarwar.
Wasu daga cikin mutanen da suka mutu 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
A cikin shekaru goma, gundumar kudancin New York ba ta sake yin shari'ar da ta shafi hukuncin kisa ba.
An samu wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da laifin kashe wasu masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi biyu, kuma a karshe an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekara ta 1953 ne aka yi hukuncin kisa a New York a kan wani laifi da aka yi a tarayya. An hukunta Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke wa hukuncin kisa shekaru biyu da suka shige don yin leƙen asiri ga Soviet Union.
An kashe Rosenberg biyu a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, wanda aka haifa a Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin tuba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
Ya bayyana wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi, in ji 'yan sanda.
Saipov ya bayyana wa hukumomi cewa ya samu wahayi zuwa ga aikata wannan laifi ne bayan da ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, a cewar tuhumar.
Ya kuma bukaci a rataye tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin sa, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan tuhume-tuhume 22 da ake masa.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin da ke kare Saipov ya ce "a bayyane yake cewa mun yi takaici" da hukuncin da aka yanke.
Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar laifin da aka yi a madadin ɗaurin rai da rai ba tare da samun damar sakewa ba zai ƙara ɓata rayuwar duk wanda ya shiga lamarin ba, in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov ta nemi masu gabatar da kara da su daina neman hukuncin kisa.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Conservative ya bukaci a dage tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya sha alwashin amfani da 'ikon jama'a' a yau a wani zanga-zangar da aka gudanar a taron 'yan majalisa na Tories.
Tsohon shugaban jam'iyyar Ukip ya bayyana cewa 'yan siyasa suna bukatar su "ji matsin lamba" daga masu shakkar kudin Euro, yayin da wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Theresa May ya ba da shawarar cewa Farage ya jagoranci tattaunawar da EU.
Mai ba da shawara a kan harkokin siyasa mai suna Peter Bone ya bayyana wa masu zanga-zangar a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya "za ta riga ta fita" idan Farage ya zama ministan Brexit.
Matsalar da May ke fuskanta wajen sulhunta jam'iyyarta da ke fama da rikici ta kara tsanantawa ne bayan da wasu 'yan jam'iyyarta da ke goyon bayan ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin EU suka halarci wani zanga-zangar nuna adawa da Brexit da aka yi a birnin.
Firaministar na fama da matsalar ci gaba da shirin sulhunta Chequers duk da hare-haren da magoya bayan Brexit, masu adawa da Brexit da EU ke kaiwa.
Abokan hulda sun nace cewa duk da rashin jin daɗi, ta ci gaba da ƙoƙarin kulla yarjejeniya da Brussels, don haka tilasta masu shakkar Euro da jam'iyyar adawa ta Labour su zaɓi tsakanin kunshin su da chaos.
Bone ya bayyana a zanga-zangar Leave Means Leave a Solihull cewa Chequers ya kamata a ajiye su a kan shara.
Ya ce ya kamata a nada Farage a matsayin mai kula da harkokin kasuwanci da kuma sanya shi a matsayin mai kula da harkokin kasuwanci da Brussels.
Idan shi ne ke da alhakin wannan, to, da mun riga mun fita, in ji shi.
Dan majalisar Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Zan goyi bayan Brexit, amma Chequers na cikin shara".
Ya bayyana rashin amincewarsa da Tarayyar Turai, ya ce: "Ba mu yi yaƙi a yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya don mu zama masu biyayya ba.
Muna son mu kafa dokokinmu a ƙasarmu.
Bone ya yi watsi da ikirarin cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun bayan zaben raba gardama na 2016: Ganin cewa mutanen Burtaniya sun canza ra'ayinsu kuma yanzu suna son ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin EU ba daidai ba ne.
'Yar jam'iyyar Conservative ta Brexit Andrea Jenkyns ma ta halarci zanga-zangar, inda ta shaida wa manema labarai cewa: "Ina cewa kawai, 'Ya firaminista, ki saurari jama'a.
Ba a son sasantawar a cikin jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su jefa kuri'a a kanta ba, ba a son ta a cikin jam'iyyarmu da kuma 'yan gwagwarmayarmu waɗanda ke tafiya a kan tituna kuma suna tabbatar da cewa an zabe mu.
Don Allah ku daina yin amfani da waɗannan kalmomin kuma ku soma saurarawa.
A wata sanarwa da ta aikawa May, ta ci gaba da cewa: "Firai ministoci za su ci gaba da aiki idan suka cika alkawuransu".
Farage ya bayyana a wani jawabi cewa 'yan siyasa dole ne su ji matsin lamba idan suna kokarin yin magudi a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
Farage ya ce, "Wannan batun amincewa ne tsakaninmu, jama'a da kuma 'yan siyasa".
Kuna kokarin yaudarar Brexit, kuma shi ya sa muke nan a yau don gaya muku cewa ba za ku samu kuɓuta ba.
Ya ci gaba da cewa a gaban taron masu farin ciki, "Ina so ku nuna wa 'yan siyasarmu matsin lamba, wadanda ke gab da cin amanar Brexit.
Za mu yi amfani da karfin mutanen wannan kasa da suka taimaka mana wajen lashe kuri'ar raba gardama kuma ba za mu taba yin tsit ba har sai mun zama 'yanci, mulkin kai, da kuma alfahari da Birtaniya.
A daidai lokacin, masu adawa da Brexit sun yi tafiya a Birmingham kafin su gudanar da zanga-zangar tsawon awa biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
Wasu 'yan gwagwarmaya sun yi amfani da tuta na kungiyar Tories Against Brexit, wata kungiya ta masu adawa da Brexit a cikin jam'iyyar May, wadda aka kaddamar a karshen mako.
Lord Adonis, wani dan jam'iyyar Labour, ya yi ba'a game da 'yan Tory da suka fuskanci matsalar tsaro a wani manhajar jam'iyyar a lokacin da suka bude taron.
