Ƙungiyar 'yan wasa ta Elite: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallo biyu a raga a wasan da Giants ta yi da Dundee
Dundee Stars sun rama rashin nasarar da suka sha a gasar Elite League a ranar Juma'a da suka sha a kan Belfast Giants ta hanyar cin nasara da ci 5 da 3 a wasan da aka yi a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun ci gaba da ci biyu a raga bayan da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier suka ci kwallo.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun daidaita wasan da suka yi a gida kafin Dwyer ya sake kafa wa Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya daidaita wasan da Dundee ta ci kafin Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ci kwallo biyu ya tabbatar da nasara.
Wannan shi ne karo na uku da 'yan Adam Keefe suka yi da Dundee a ranar Jumma'a da dare 2-1 a Belfast, rashin nasara a gasar Elite League a wannan kakar.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na hudu da kungiyoyin biyu suka kara a kakar bana, inda Giants ta lashe wasannin uku da ta gabata.
Dwyer ya fara bugawa kungiyar kwallo a minti na hudu bayan da ta yi kasa da 3:35 bayan da Kendall McFaull ya buga kwallo.
A wannan lokaci mai ban sha'awa, Sullivan ya dawo da 'yan wasan gida a wasan bayan 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya taimaka wa Cownie a raga a 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da jagorancin Giants kafin hutun rabin lokaci lokacin da ya zira kwallo ta biyu a daren kafin karshen rabin farko.
Kungiyar da ke gida ta sake tsarawa kuma Bouchard ya sake daidaitawa tare da burin wasan wuta a minti na 28.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun haɗu don taimakawa Nielsen don sa Dundee ta jagoranci wasan a karo na farko a ƙarshen rabi na biyu.
Giants, da suka yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu a cikin biyar da suka gabata, za su buga wasansu na gida a filin wasa na Milton Keynes a ranar Juma'a mai zuwa.
Wani matukin jirgi ya mutu bayan ya tabbatar da cewa daruruwan mutane a cikin jirgin sama sun tsere wa girgizar kasa
