Turai ta yi nasara a gasar cin kofin Ryder ta Paris
Team Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018 kuma ta doke Team USA da ci 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National kusa da Paris.
Yanzu Amurka ta sha kaye sau shida a jere a Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe kofin bayan tawagar da ta jagoranci Thomas Bjorn ta Denmark ta samu maki 14.5 da ta bukata domin doke Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala a tsawon gasar, ya nutse a cikin ruwa a filin wasa na 16 (par 3) kuma ya rasa Francesco Molinari.
Molinari dan wasan Italiya ya yi fice a dukkan wasanninsa, ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da gasar ta fara a shekarar 1979.
An doke dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth da ci 5 da 4 daga hannun dan wasan da ya fi kasa a tawagar Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen daga Denmark.
Dan wasan da ya fi kowacce kungiya a duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya sha kashi 2 da 1 a hannun Ian Poulter na Ingila, wanda zai iya zama Ryder Cup na karshe.
